{"componentChunkName":"component---theme-src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/getting-started","webpackCompilationHash":"d8e72fdba038183d0b0b","result":{"data":{"post":{"headings":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"Getting started","path":"/getting-started","tags":["Theme"],"excerpt":"Nehalem is easy to install due to its packaged nature. Learn how to install it and the basics of the configuration capabilities.","created":"2019-07-30T00:00:00.000Z","createdPretty":"30 July, 2019","updated":"2019-07-30T00:00:00.000Z","updatedPretty":"30 July, 2019","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.4997845756139594,"src":"/gatsby-blog/static/e7dd834504c9cac54f64c575b529524e/57238/cover.jpg","srcSet":"/gatsby-blog/static/e7dd834504c9cac54f64c575b529524e/5398f/cover.jpg 200w,\n/gatsby-blog/static/e7dd834504c9cac54f64c575b529524e/26a4d/cover.jpg 400w,\n/gatsby-blog/static/e7dd834504c9cac54f64c575b529524e/57238/cover.jpg 800w,\n/gatsby-blog/static/e7dd834504c9cac54f64c575b529524e/23dde/cover.jpg 1200w,\n/gatsby-blog/static/e7dd834504c9cac54f64c575b529524e/526a4/cover.jpg 1600w,\n/gatsby-blog/static/e7dd834504c9cac54f64c575b529524e/799a5/cover.jpg 3481w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"html":"<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Important</strong>: Before diving right into the installation check the <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/themes/using-a-gatsby-theme\">Using a Gatsby Theme</a> guide!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>Install the theme via npm or yarn:</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i @nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem --save\n<span class=\"token comment\"># or</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> @nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Add the theme theme to your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>:</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">@nehalist/gatsby-theme-nehalem</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// optional theme options</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// location to our content</span>\n        contentPath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">content</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// the page manifest</span>\n        manifest<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">nehalem - A Gatsby theme</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          short_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">nehalem</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          start_url<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          background_color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">#a4cbb8</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          theme_color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">#a4cbb8</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          display<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">minimal-ui</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          icon<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>__dirname<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">/assets/nehalist-gatsby.png</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// if archive pages should be generated automatically</span>\n        loadDefaultPages<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// posts shown on the front page</span>\n        postsPerPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><em>Note: In a future release theme options will cover most configurations of the <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>!</em></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<p>Nehalem in its default configuration requires a certain structure of your content. This is especially important to consider\nwhen using a starter which already ships with a specific content structure - so just follow these rules:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Be sure to have a <code class=\"language-text\">content</code> directory within your Gatsby installation</li>\n<li>Be sure to have a <code class=\"language-text\">tags.yml</code> file within the <code class=\"language-text\">content</code> directory with <em>at least</em> one tag, e.g.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Uncategorized\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#000</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">icon</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token null important\">null</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">featured</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">false</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Be sure for your markdown files to include proper frontmatter content, e.g.:</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token hr punctuation\">---</span>\ntitle: \"Post title\"\npath: \"/path-to-your-post\"\ntags: [\"Theme\"]\nfeaturedImage: \"./cover.jpg\"\nexcerpt: Descriptive description.\ncreated: 2019-07-29\n<span class=\"token title important\">updated: 2019-07-29\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">---</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>For further instructions check the other docs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"creating-content\">How to create posts and pages</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby-blog/customization\">How to customize the theme</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby-blog/custom-pages\">How to create custom pages</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Or check the <a href=\"/gatsby-blog/features\">features</a> to get an idea of all the possibilities with Nehalem!</p>\n<p>I hope you enjoy this theme!</p>\n<p>â€“ Kevin</p>\n<hr>\n<p><em>Cover by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@bradencollum\">@brandencollum</a></em></p>"},"primaryTag":{"name":"Theme","color":null}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"postId":"e18fa0ec-c72f-52c2-ad1a-a5a872929e0a","primaryTag":"Theme"}}}